import React from 'react' import './MainWeather.css' const MainWeather = (props) => { const {weather} = props const toFahrenheit = () => { const temp = weather.main.temp const fah = (temp - 273.15) * 1.8 + 32 return fah } return (

{weather.name}, {weather.sys.country}

{weather.weather[0].main}

88°

{weather.weather[0].description}

Min: 87°

Max: 92°

) } export default MainWeather
